将方程(\ref{eq1})(\ref{eq2})(\ref{eq3})整理为矩阵形式，得到
/*
\begin{equation} \label{eq4}
\begin{aligned}
\frac{dx}{dt}&=D(x)(r+Ax) \\
&=
\begin{pmatrix}
x_1 & 0 & 0 \\ 
0 & x_2 & 0 \\ 
0 & 0 & x_3 \\ 
\end{pmatrix}
\left(\begin{pmatrix}
r_1  \\ 
-r_2 \\ 
-r_3 \\ 
\end{pmatrix}
+
\begin{pmatrix}
-\alpha_1 & -\gamma_{12} & 0 \\ 
e_{12}\gamma_{12} & -\alpha_2 & -\gamma_{23} \\ 
0 & e_{23}\gamma_{23} & -\alpha_3 \\ 
